---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Recverse — Modern AI & IT Delivery for SMBs"
  description="AI MVPs, ERP-adjacent delivery, IT project management, and modern web presence. Clear scope, clean delivery, measurable outcomes."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <div class="kicker">AI · Delivery · Project Management</div>
      <h1 class="h1">Modern solutions that actually ship.</h1>
      <p class="p">
        Recverse helps SMBs move into the modern era: AI MVPs, ERP-adjacent implementation, and IT project management — lean,
        transparent, and reliable. No overengineering.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=Brainstorming">Start a brainstorm</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/en/services/">View services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-tight">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
          <h2 class="h2">Clear scope</h2>
          <p class="p">We define goals, risks, dependencies, and a deliverable MVP quickly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
          <h2 class="h2">Clean delivery</h2>
          <p class="p">Lean engineering, documented decisions, and a proper handover.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
          <h2 class="h2">Measurable impact</h2>
          <p class="p">Outcome-focused: less manual effort, lower risk, better quality.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="kicker">Anonymized case highlights</div>
      <h2 class="h2" style="margin-top:10px;">Three typical projects — baseline → approach → outcome</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top:18px;">
        <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
          <h3 style="margin:0; font-weight:900;">Deploy, build, and connect AI tools</h3>
          <p class="p"><strong>Baseline:</strong> Fragmented tools/workflows, high manual coordination overhead.</p>
          <p class="p"><strong>Approach:</strong> Prioritized use cases, lightweight integration setup, clear governance & handover.</p>
          <p class="p"><strong>Outcome:</strong> ~20–30% less manual effort and more stable operations.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
          <h3 style="margin:0; font-weight:900;">ERP delivery & AI enablement</h3>
          <p class="p"><strong>Baseline:</strong> Many stakeholders, interface risk, unclear ownership.</p>
          <p class="p"><strong>Approach:</strong> Delivery plan, interface-level view, pilot AI use case embedded in the process.</p>
          <p class="p"><strong>Outcome:</strong> Less rework, lower risk at critical handoffs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
          <h3 style="margin:0; font-weight:900;">Website renewal / SEO foundation</h3>
          <p class="p"><strong>Baseline:</strong> Outdated site, poor performance, low trust and weak conversion.</p>
          <p class="p"><strong>Approach:</strong> Modern redesign, clear information architecture, technical SEO essentials.</p>
          <p class="p"><strong>Outcome:</strong> Faster load times, cleaner conversion path, better visibility baseline.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top:18px;" class="muted">
        Note: anonymized. Numbers are indicative ranges and depend on baseline conditions.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-tight">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="kicker">How we work</div>
      <h2 class="h2" style="margin-top:10px;">Your idea → brainstorm → proposal</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top:18px;">
        <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
          <h3 style="margin:0; font-weight:900;">1) Brainstorm (short & concrete)</h3>
          <p class="p">Goal, context, risks, constraints, success criteria.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
          <h3 style="margin:0; font-weight:900;">2) Scope & delivery plan</h3>
          <p class="p">What gets delivered, in what order, including dependencies.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
          <h3 style="margin:0; font-weight:900;">3) Proposal</h3>
          <p class="p">A concrete, transparent, executable offer.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-actions" style="margin-top:18px;">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=Brainstorming">Start a brainstorm</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/en/services/">View services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
